The paper deals with the semantics of argumentation graphs, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It also involves the computation of weights and aggregation functions, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA). The paper also discusses convergence and divergence theorems, which are related to algorithms and data structures (cs.DS) and computational complexity (cs.CC).
